# bat — used as cat replacement and as MANPAGER.
# TwoDark is the closest built-in to the cobalt/magenta-on-black aesthetic.
# Run `bat --list-themes` to browse alternatives, then change here.
--theme="TwoDark"
--style="numbers,changes,header"
--map-syntax="*.jenkinsfile:Groovy"
--map-syntax="*.props:Java Properties"
--paging=auto
